Combat

Encounter
  -Contains the Creatures that will join the turn based combat.
  -Split damage taken in the open world between all the creatures in this encounter.

EncounterManager
  -Static script.
  -Keeps track of the creatures that are joining battle and the instigator aswell as the ability that started the combat.
  -Communicates with BattleManager.

BattleManager
  -Keeps track of whose turn it is.
  -Win and lose condition.
